text: Victoria Williams (born 28 March 1968) is a British female barebow archer. She won the bronze medal at the 2014 World Field Archery Championships in the women's team event. She was Barebow 50+ Women champion. She was a coach for team Great Britain. Her review appeared in Barebow International. == References == Category:1968 births Category:British archers Category:Living people
